{"tid":216485,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"全球2016軍費增加      中國佔亞洲一半","createTime":"2017-04-25T08:11:19.000Z","updateTime":"2017-04-26T10:12:50.000Z","uid":58099,"like":2,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"7630bcdb5ad11c2cbf0b74c01af155cd0981b1f5","tid":216485,"uid":58099,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-25T08:11:19.000Z","msg":"追蹤全球軍事開支的瑞典斯德哥爾摩國際和平研究所（SIPRI）最新公布，2016年全球軍事支出總額年增0.4%，亞太地區成長最快，其中中國是亞太地區最大軍事支出國，佔48%。<br />\n<br />\nSIPRI官網24日發出新聞稿公布，2016年全球軍事支出增至1兆6860億美元，較2015年微增0.4%，占全球國內生產毛額（GDP）2.2%。<br />\n<br />\n據新聞稿，美國仍是全球年度軍費最高的國家，2016年軍事支出年增1.7%，達到6110億美元；中國大陸軍費是全球第二高，2016年軍事支出年增10.3%，達到2150億美元。<br />\n<br />\n報告指出，中國是亞洲最大的軍事支出國，占亞太地區軍費的48%。這個崛起中的超級大國2016年軍費支出約為2150億美元，幾乎是印度的4倍。這兩個國家共佔該地區軍費的60%。"},{"pid":"8872f94e1a67d72f19261dbd8b413376edebd94f","tid":216485,"uid":58099,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-25T08:12:43.000Z","msg":"中國有錢到痴線<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4d74328767aca0bbd19c219a524c3f18b5ec6114","tid":216485,"uid":58099,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-25T08:22:30.000Z","msg":"."},{"pid":"83ad37e0c655f701baf54e7513d470f29ed08356","tid":216485,"uid":32676,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-25T09:23:35.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>中國有錢到痴線<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n據新聞稿，美國仍是全球年度軍費最高的國家，2016年軍事支出年增1.7%，達到6110億美元<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"20aba480749dee2d913b98962fce9e763edbf4a6","tid":216485,"uid":57376,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-25T09:24:54.000Z","msg":"清朝夠亞洲第一啦<br />\n結果？<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7acdf0e8813cd2764352161e9e2ea923a7b4cc4c","tid":216485,"uid":58099,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-25T10:00:13.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>中國有錢到痴線<img src=\"